
Version 1.0
- Three roles: admin, editor, viewer.
- Support multiples LDAPs (Open Ldap, MS Active Directory, Notes Domino) or local database for authentication, and CAS.
- Can talk with SQLite, PostgreSQL, MySQL, MSSQL, FireBird, Oracle, IBM DB2, etc.
- Full users accountability: open session, time zone and IPs request, etc.
- Multi views for the back end frontend design.
- Custom email templates for sending notification to the users.
- Custom error pages...
- All static pages can be rendered in one function.
- Support editing for multi languges.
- Optimize SEO